            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2411Step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potato cakes are cooking, add the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> to a large bowl with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> then add it to the dressing and give it a gentle mix up</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
