        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan with the <strong>remaining chorizo</strong> to a medium-low heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, crack your <strong>eggs</strong> into the pan on the opposite side to the chorizo</p><p>Cook, covered for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2411Step-7-x200.jpg",
